{#
/**
 * @file
 * Co-working introduction wizard markup (dashboard and start page).
 *
 * Variables:
 * - intro_asset_base: Base URL for module SVGs.
 * - intro_connected_accounts_url: Connected Accounts URL.
 *
 * @ingroup themeable
 */
#}
<div id="scs-manager--coworking-intro" class="scs-manager--coworking-intro fixed inset-0 z-[60] flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-950/70 p-4" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="scs-manager--coworking-intro-title" data-coworking-intro-root>
  <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-panel bg-white rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-[min(900px,max(200px,50vw))] max-w-full overflow-hidden flex flex-col border border-stone-200">
    <div class="px-6 pt-6 pb-2 border-b border-stone-100 relative">
      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-skip-row">
      <button type="button" class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-skip z-10 text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-800 underline text-end max-w-[min(12rem,42%)] leading-snug" data-coworking-intro-skip>{{ 'Skip introduction'|t }}</button>
      </div>
      <h2 id="scs-manager--coworking-intro-title" class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 w-full max-w-full text-center pe-36 sm:pe-40">{{ 'Welcome to the Semantic Co-Working Space'|t }}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-scroll-body min-h-0 flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-6 text-stone-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide" data-coworking-intro-slide="0">
        <p class="text-base font-medium text-stone-900 mb-3">{{ 'Welcome'|t }}</p>
        <p class="mb-3">{{ 'Here you find all tools to support your work through the collection data life cycle – from capture and cleaning to publishing of FAIR and linked data.'|t }}</p>
        <p>{{ 'The next steps highlight some features and help with the initial configuration and setup a WissKI environment.'|t }}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide" data-coworking-intro-slide="1">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 p-3">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">{{ 'Manager of Services and Projects.'|t }}</p>
            <p>{{ 'The Semantic Co-Working Space (SCS) provides selected applications for digital collection management. The SCS is the main access point to these applications and you can manage them in a user-friendly webinterface. The SCS is build to work together, so our main services support collaborative work and data integration between applications. You can easily share the access to your applications with other SCS users. You also find some information about the services and get help, if you are stuck.'|t }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide" data-coworking-intro-slide="2">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 p-3">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">{{ 'Your Dashboard'|t }}</p>
            <p>{{ 'The Dashboard helps to manage your applications. Clicking on the application name will open the application in a new tab. Here you can create your own WissKI environment to manage your collection data, deploy a relational database or triplestore. The cards show the health status, and you can access the corresponding documentation pages and gain some more information on the application page.'|t }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide" data-coworking-intro-slide="3">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure--stack flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 p-3">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">{{ 'Projekt management'|t }}</p>
            <p>{{ 'You can share the access to your applications with other SCS users by assigning them to projects. If someone add you to a project, you will receive an email notification and can accept or reject the invitation.'|t }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide" data-coworking-intro-slide="4">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure--stack flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 p-3">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">{{ 'Account management'|t }}</p>
            <p>{{ 'Manage your account settings, language and region, connected accounts and SCS Manager Settings (where you can reset this wizard by the way).'|t }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide" data-coworking-intro-slide="5">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-app-slide-figure flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-stone-100 border border-stone-200 p-3">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">{{ 'Need help?'|t }}</p>
            <p>{{ 'We have a extensive <a href="/soda-scs-manager/documentation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">documentation</a>, where you find useful information and tutorials. Still get stuck? Contact our SCS support team at <a href="mailto:scs-manager@sammlungen.io">scs-manager@sammlungen.io</a>. '|t }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden" data-coworking-intro-slide="6">
        <p class="text-base font-medium text-stone-900 mb-3">{{ 'Connect Nextcloud'|t }}</p>
        <p class="mb-4">{{ 'A working Nextcloud connection is necessary so data and files can flow between WissKI and your other applications. Start the connection here, or later from your account settings.'|t }}</p>
        <div class="scs-manager--nextcloud-connect-wrapper scs-manager--nextcloud-connect-inline rounded-lg border border-stone-200 p-4 bg-stone-50">
          <button type="button" class="scs-manager--nextcloud-connect-btn w-full px-4 py-3 mb-4 bg-stone-800 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-stone-500 focus:ring-offset-2">{{ 'Connect Nextcloud'|t }}</button>
          <p class="scs-manager--nextcloud-connect-status-inline mb-3 text-sm" data-status="unknown">{{ 'Checking connection…'|t }}</p>
          <p class="scs-manager--nextcloud-connect-fallback-hint text-xs text-stone-600">{{ 'Allow popups for this site when prompted. If login fails, try again or use Connected Accounts below.'|t }}</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-stone-600">{{ 'For OpenID / SSO account linking:'|t }} <a href="{{ intro_connected_accounts_url }}" class="text-blue-700 underline hover:text-blue-900">{{ 'Open Connected Accounts'|t }}</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden" data-coworking-intro-slide="7">
          <p class="text-base font-medium text-stone-900 mb-3">{{ 'Create your first WissKI Environment'|t }}</p>
          <p class="mb-3">{{ 'We create a complete environment: database, triplestore, and WissKI. Provisioning starts immediately and may take several minutes.'|t }}</p>
        <label for="scs-manager--coworking-intro-wisski-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-800 mb-1">{{ 'WissKI name'|t }}</label>
        <p id="scs-manager--coworking-intro-wisski-name-hint" class="text-xs text-stone-500 mb-2">{{ 'Use at most 25 characters: letters (A–Z, a–z), digits (0–9), and spaces. No other symbols.'|t }}</p>
        <input id="scs-manager--coworking-intro-wisski-name" type="text" class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-stone-900 mb-1 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-stone-200 focus:border-stone-400" maxlength="25" autocomplete="off" data-coworking-intro-wisski-name placeholder="{{ 'e.g. My collection workspace'|t }}" aria-describedby="scs-manager--coworking-intro-wisski-name-hint" />
        <p id="scs-manager--coworking-intro-wisski-name-error" class="text-sm text-red-700 font-medium mb-3" data-coworking-intro-wisski-error role="alert" aria-live="polite" hidden></p>
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center gap-2 py-2.5">
            <button type="button" class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-btn-create-wisski px-4 py-2 text-white text-sm rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#e68500] focus:ring-offset-2" data-coworking-intro-open-wisski>{{ 'Create WissKI Environment'|t }}</button>
          <button type="button" class="px-4 py-2 border border-stone-300 text-sm rounded hover:bg-stone-50" data-coworking-intro-finish>{{ 'Finish without creating'|t }}</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-slide hidden" data-coworking-intro-slide="8" data-coworking-intro-success-slide>
          <p class="scs-manager--coworking-intro-success-title text-base font-semibold mb-3">{{ 'WissKI Environment created'|t }}</p>
        <p class="mb-3" data-coworking-intro-success-summary></p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-stone-600">{{ 'Provisioning can take several minutes. You can monitor the applications Health Status from your dashboard or open the details page now.'|t }}</p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-block mb-4 text-blue-700 underline hover:text-blue-900 text-sm font-medium" data-coworking-intro-success-details-link>{{ 'Open application details'|t }}</a>
        <div>
          <button type="button" class="px-4 py-2 bg-stone-800 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-stone-900" data-coworking-intro-close-success>{{ 'Close introduction'|t }}</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-6 py-4 border-t border-stone-100 bg-stone-50 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
      <p class="text-xs text-stone-500" data-coworking-intro-step-label aria-live="polite"></p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <button type="button" class="px-4 py-2 border border-stone-300 text-sm rounded hover:bg-white disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" data-coworking-intro-back disabled>{{ 'Back'|t }}</button>
        <button type="button" class="px-4 py-2 bg-stone-800 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-stone-900 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" data-coworking-intro-next>{{ 'Next'|t }}</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
